---
// About component - Diseño 3 (Retro Classic Style)
---

<section class="about" id="about">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="retro-section-header">
			<h2 class="retro-title">
				<span class="title-bracket">[</span>
				SOBRE MÍ
				<span class="title-bracket">]</span>
			</h2>
		</div>
		
		<div class="retro-content">
			<div class="retro-text-panel">
				<div class="panel-header">
					<span class="panel-label">INFO.TXT</span>
				</div>
				<div class="panel-content">
					<p class="text-line">
						<span class="line-number">01</span>
						<span class="text-content">Desarrollador full stack con pasión por crear soluciones tecnológicas innovadoras.</span>
					</p>
					<p class="text-line">
						<span class="line-number">02</span>
						<span class="text-content">Mi experiencia abarca desde el front-end hasta el back-end, permitiéndome</span>
					</p>
					<p class="text-line">
						<span class="line-number">03</span>
						<span class="text-content">construir aplicaciones completas y escalables.</span>
					</p>
					<p class="text-line">
						<span class="line-number">04</span>
						<span class="text-content"></span>
					</p>
					<p class="text-line">
						<span class="line-number">05</span>
						<span class="text-content">Especializado en arquitectura de software, bases de datos y APIs RESTful.</span>
					</p>
					<p class="text-line">
						<span class="line-number">06</span>
						<span class="text-content">Trabajo con tecnologías modernas como Node.js, Python, React y sistemas</span>
					</p>
					<p class="text-line">
						<span class="line-number">07</span>
						<span class="text-content">en la nube para entregar productos de alta calidad.</span>
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="retro-stats-panel">
				<div class="panel-header">
					<span class="panel-label">STATS.DAT</span>
				</div>
				<div class="stats-grid">
					<div class="stat-box">
						<div class="stat-value">75+</div>
						<div class="stat-label">PROYECTOS</div>
						<div class="stat-bar">
							<div class="stat-fill" style="width: 85%"></div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="stat-box">
						<div class="stat-value">5+</div>
						<div class="stat-label">AÑOS</div>
						<div class="stat-bar">
							<div class="stat-fill" style="width: 70%"></div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="stat-box">
						<div class="stat-value">30+</div>
						<div class="stat-label">CLIENTES</div>
						<div class="stat-bar">
							<div class="stat-fill" style="width: 75%"></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.about {
		padding: 5rem 2rem;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2a2a2a 0%, #1a1a1a 100%);
		position: relative;
	}

	.about::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		bottom: 0;
		background-image: 
			repeating-linear-gradient(
				45deg,
				transparent,
				transparent 10px,
				rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.03) 10px,
				rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.03) 20px
			);
		pointer-events: none;
	}

	.container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.retro-section-header {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.retro-title {
		font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		color: #ff8c00;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 4px;
		text-shadow: 
			0 0 10px #ff8c00,
			0 0 20px rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.5);
	}

	.title-bracket {
		color: #00ff00;
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin: 0 0.5rem;
	}

	.retro-content {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.retro-text-panel,
	.retro-stats-panel {
		background: #0a0a0a;
		border: 4px solid #ff8c00;
		box-shadow: 
			0 0 0 2px #1a1a1a,
			0 0 20px rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.3),
			inset 0 0 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
		position: relative;
	}

	.panel-header {
		background: #ff8c00;
		padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
		border-bottom: 2px solid #1a1a1a;
	}

	.panel-label {
		font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-weight: bold;
		color: #000;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 2px;
	}

	.panel-content {
		padding: 1.5rem;
		font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
	}

	.text-line {
		display: flex;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.line-number {
		color: #666;
		margin-right: 1rem;
		min-width: 30px;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
	}

	.text-content {
		color: #ffd700;
		flex: 1;
	}

	.stats-grid {
		padding: 1.5rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.stat-box {
		background: rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.1);
		border: 2px solid #ff8c00;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.stat-value {
		font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: bold;
		color: #00ff00;
		text-shadow: 0 0 10px #00ff00;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.stat-label {
		font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: #ff8c00;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 2px;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.stat-bar {
		height: 8px;
		background: #1a1a1a;
		border: 1px solid #ff8c00;
		overflow: hidden;
		position: relative;
	}

	.stat-fill {
		height: 100%;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00ff00 0%, #ff8c00 100%);
		box-shadow: 0 0 10px #00ff00;
		animation: fillBar 1.5s ease-out;
	}

	@keyframes fillBar {
		from { width: 0; }
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.retro-content {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.retro-title {
			font-size: 1.8rem;
		}

		.title-bracket {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}
	}
</style>
